---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Services - Kate Career Coach"
    description="Coaching services to help you navigate your career journey with confidence"
>
    <div class="mt-20 py-16 min-h-screen">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <p class="font-handwritten text-2xl text-accent mb-4">
                    What I Offer
                </p>
                <h1
                    class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-foreground mb-6"
                >
                    Coaching Services
                </h1>
                <p
                    class="font-sans text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto"
                >
                    Choose the path that fits your needs. Every journey is
                    different, and I'm here to support yours.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
                <div
                    class="bg-card p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors flex flex-col group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-handwritten text-xl text-foreground group-hover:text-primary-foreground transition-colors"
                            >1</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-foreground mb-4">
                        The Pivot Program
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-sans text-muted-foreground mb-6">
                        This focused 3-month package is designed for clients who are ready to make significant progress in a shorter time frame. Over 6 sessions, we’ll dive into your key challenges, set actionable goals, and create a clear path to achieve them. This package offers a balanced approach to achieving meaningful change with consistent support.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8 flex-grow">
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>Weekly 70-minute sessions
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>Email support between sessions
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>Personalized action plans
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span> €610 
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="/intro-call"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&_svg]:pointer-events-none [&_svg]:size-4 [&_svg]:shrink-0 h-10 px-4 py-2 bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-primary-foreground font-sans rounded-full w-full"
                        >Learn More</a
                    >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="bg-card p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors flex flex-col group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-handwritten text-xl text-foreground group-hover:text-primary-foreground transition-colors"
                            >2</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-foreground mb-4">
                        The Clarity Program
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-sans text-muted-foreground mb-6">
                        Across 3 focused sessions, we identify what’s actually blocking you, cut through noise and overthinking, and turn ambiguity into a clear, realistic action plan.

This is for moments when staying stuck is more expensive than deciding.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8 flex-grow">
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>4-week intensive program
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>Values & strengths assessment
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>Future vision mapping
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span> €340
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="/intro-call"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&_svg]:pointer-events-none [&_svg]:size-4 [&_svg]:shrink-0 h-10 px-4 py-2 bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-primary-foreground font-sans rounded-full w-full"
                        >Learn More</a
                    >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="bg-card p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors flex flex-col group"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary transition-colors"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-handwritten text-xl text-foreground group-hover:text-primary-foreground transition-colors"
                            >3</span
                        >
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-foreground mb-4">
                        One-off session
                    </h2>
                    <p class="font-sans text-muted-foreground mb-6">
                        This offering is perfect for one-off requests such as resolving urgent challenges, identifying and leveraging key resources, preparing for an important talk/interview or developing a clear action plan for your next steps.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8 flex-grow">
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>Resume & LinkedIn optimization
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>Interview preparation
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>Networking strategies
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-2"
                        >
                            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"
                            ></span>€120
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <a
                        href="/intro-call"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&_svg]:pointer-events-none [&_svg]:size-4 [&_svg]:shrink-0 h-10 px-4 py-2 bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 text-primary-foreground font-sans rounded-full w-full"
                        >Learn More</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
